ure became more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705197,"age":60,"year":"1455","julianDay":2252488,"title":"Wars of the Roses","description":"Wars of the Roses was a series of English civil wars for control of the throne of England between the royal families House of Lancaster and the House of York. The name of the war was derived as the red rose was the symbol of the Lancastrians and the white rose was the symbol of the Yorks.","url":"https://www.history.com/topics/british-history/wars-of-the-roses","urlTitle":"History - Wars of the Roses","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. William Chichele was born about 1395, in London, Middlesex, England. She had at least 4 sons and 4 daughters with William Chichele, II."},"et":{"about 1395–":"umbes 1395–Surnud","1394–1451":"1394–1451","1412–1455":"1412–1455","1413–1447":"1413–1447","1415–Female":"1415–Surnud","1416–1444":"1416–1444","1419–Male":"1419–Surnud","1420–1453":"1420–1453","1421–1461":"1421–1461","1425–Female":"1425–Surnud","1395–Female":"1395–Surnud","1451":"1451","1395":"1395","1461":"1461","1394":"1394","1415":"1415","1425":"1425","1447":"1447","1413":"1413","1412":"1412","1444":"1444","1455":"1455","1421":"1421","15 February 1412":"15. veebruar 1412","1420":"1420","1453":"1453","1419":"1419","about 1395":"umbes 1395","1416":"1416","London, Middlesex, England":"London, Middlesex, England","Wimpole, Cambridgeshire, England":"Wimpole, Cambridgeshire, England","Canterbury, Kent, England":"Canterbury, Kent, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1395–":"noin 1395–Kuollut","1394–1451":"1394–1451","1412–1455":"1412–1455","1413–1447":"1413–1447","1415–Female":"1415–Kuollut","1416–1444":"1416–1444","1419–Male":"1419–Kuollut","1420–1453":"1420–1453","1421–1461":"1421–1461","1425–Female":"1425–Kuollut","1395–Female":"1395–Kuollut","1451":"1451","1395":"1395","1461":"1461","1394":"1394","1415":"1415","1425":"1425","1447":"1447","1413":"1413"